_sText: you find yourself on a cloud, across the cloud is the opposing team.  Fighting your way to the middle you see a button and a door.  You hit the button, an alarm goes off, and it doesnt sound good.  You try to find a way to free yourself of the almost certain impending doom.  Hark, whats that?  The door begins to open with a beautiful sound.  Past the door is a ladder, a ladder that goes up, wayyyyy up.  You begin to climb wondering whats at the top...
